page.title: 06**********Cub Scouts********
page.content:
Cubs is held on Mondays from 6:15 pm to 7:30 pm. There are 8 cubs in the pack. the leader is an oldish man who isn't very active. We play games like man the ship,man the life boat,shrimps,whales, and non stop cricket. The cub scout hut was built on chapel land. Inside the hut there is a kitchen and a main hall. In the kitchen there is a cooker, sink, table, plates, cups, knives, and forks.In the main hall there is the pack's flag chairs and tables. We pay subs to cover expenses like badges, uniforms e.t.c.
Written by Brian Inman aged 9 yrs.
